{
  "stem": "8892.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was unreal that how clever and how smart it was.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And anyway, it comes New Year, end of New Year.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they said that I think the officer, the German soldier, the lady soldier tells somebody that yes, we are going to be leaving from there.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They must leave because the enemy, of course, was Russia coming, or-- or whoever and the bombing you could hear already around there quite a bit already, getting closer and closer.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So we are going to march.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We don't know where we're going.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We don't know the name of the camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And January until the end of January, 30 days we're on the road to get to Bergen-Belsen. 30 days, snow all over, everywhere.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Well, we're still together.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Thank God nobody died from the five of us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And anybody who couldn't march, or couldn't walk, they just left behind.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Sometimes they shot them, right there, shoot them right there in the ice, because they just couldn't walk.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They give you always, I don't know how many kilometers, we would stop for a rest.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And at certain times they would give us a ration, the bread and the margarine and some warm liquid or something.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And then each night, we would stop at a farmer.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But it always was so outskirts of a farm that you didn't see the public.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "You didn't see the people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "You know how they went to the highways, and they managed to always get around those highways were nobody.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "At one point they had to take us through a little town.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I wish I would remember the name.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Clean, shiny snow on the ground.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "We're walking by a butcher shop.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And it's all glass-- just like in the shopping here, it would be a glass front.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
